{"tid":498074,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓突然唔食罐頭","createTime":"2017-12-13T12:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T06:49:13.000Z","uid":146172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e359cc01b6f5d5c728c0609c8431cf4d77d39ce","tid":498074,"uid":146172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"E幾日隻貓突然唔食罐頭，但乾糧都會食。精神玩之類都冇咩問題，但就係比罐頭佢聞一聞就走左去，以前一開就沖住黎食宜家一啖都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇人知發生咩事？"},{"pid":"0709b8c9af442ff81b22950300b900c67f80b27a","tid":498074,"uid":162779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"真心帶去睇下醫生好啲，就咁講好難知咩事，可能真係唔舒服"},{"pid":"1687e5acceb1e938c48409444b6b33ce30ac6912","tid":498074,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"咁啱唔肚餓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇試過放係到唔理佢"},{"pid":"ab3326626ab0c7525ec1933bfb138bb73f300425","tid":498074,"uid":146172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁啱唔肚餓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇試過放係到唔理佢</blockquote><br />\n放過 成晚唔食 。今日換二個新既比佢 一隻都係唔食一隻係咁以食左幾啖"},{"pid":"886e8d9034bdd735feebc9a3182ede497a807ef3","tid":498074,"uid":146172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心帶去睇下醫生好啲，就咁講好難知咩事，可能真係唔舒服</blockquote><br />\n過兩日試多幾隻都唔食就帶佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d48e3b20e42f3a0c2f3ee00bdb37979a4f23632","tid":498074,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"肯食乾糧但唔食罐頭應該係食厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買定幾種牌子幾隻味換嚟食"},{"pid":"f5bb82c1b14665263b3b8ae